# CarbonSense Web Interface

This rule details the web interface components of the CarbonSense system.

## Web Application Components

- [src/carbonsense/web/run_server.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/web/run_server.py) - Entry point for running the web server
- [src/carbonsense/web/app.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/web/app.py) - Main FastAPI application with routes
- [src/carbonsense/web/templates/](mdc:src/carbonsense/web/templates/) - HTML templates for the dashboard
- [src/carbonsense/web/static/](mdc:src/carbonsense/web/static/) - CSS, JavaScript, and other static assets

## API Endpoints

The web interface exposes several API endpoints for:

1. Carbon footprint calculations
2. Voice query processing
3. Visualization data 
4. System configuration
5. Agent interaction

## Dashboard Features

The CarbonSense dashboard provides:

1. Carbon footprint visualization
2. Goal tracking
3. Achievement badges
4. Weekly trends analysis
5. Interactive query interface
